<section id="faqs">
  <h3
    class="text-base-content mb-4 text-lg font-semibold uppercase md:text-2xl"
  >
    Frequently Asked Questions
  </h3>
  <details
    class="bg-base-100 border-base-300 collapse-arrow collapse border"
    name="faq-accordion"
    open
  >
    <summary class="collapse-title font-semibold">
      Do you take reservations?
    </summary>
    <div class="collapse-content text-sm">
      We keep things mostly walk-in, but for parties of six or more, give us a
      call and we'll do our best to get you set up.
    </div>
  </details>
  <details
    class="bg-base-100 border-base-300 collapse-arrow collapse border"
    name="faq-accordion"
  >
    <summary class="collapse-title font-semibold">
      Do you have vegan or vegetarian options?
    </summary>
    <div class="collapse-content text-sm">
      Yes — look for the leaf icon on our food menu. We've got vegan links, a
      vegan burger, and a couple of sides that keep it plant-based.
    </div>
  </details>
  <details
    class="bg-base-100 border-base-300 collapse-arrow collapse border"
    name="faq-accordion"
  >
    <summary class="collapse-title font-semibold"> Are dogs allowed? </summary>
    <div class="collapse-content text-sm">
      Well-behaved pups are always welcome on our patio.
    </div>
  </details>
  <details
    class="bg-base-100 border-base-300 collapse-arrow collapse border"
    name="faq-accordion"
  >
    <summary class="collapse-title font-semibold">
      Is there a kids' menu?
    </summary>
    <div class="collapse-content text-sm">
      We don't have a dedicated kids' menu, but our Debreziner & Small Fries
      combo is a popular pick for younger appetites.
    </div>
  </details>
  <details
    class="bg-base-100 border-base-300 collapse-arrow collapse border"
    name="faq-accordion"
  >
    <summary class="collapse-title font-semibold">
      Do you validate parking?
    </summary>
    <div class="collapse-content text-sm">
      We don't currently offer validation, but street parking is available
      nearby, and we're a short walk from the Southport Brown Line stop.
    </div>
  </details>
  <details
    class="bg-base-100 border-base-300 collapse-arrow collapse border"
    name="faq-accordion"
  >
    <summary class="collapse-title font-semibold">
      Can I book the space for a private event?
    </summary>
    <div class="collapse-content text-sm">
      We're not currently taking private event bookings — best to give us a call
      directly if you have a specific request.
    </div>
  </details>
</section>
